Dialogue: 0,0:00:19.58,0:00:26.30,SR OP,,0000,0000,0000,,There’s something I want to tell you, but it’s too heavy
Dialogue: 0,0:00:26.30,0:00:32.18,SR OP,,0000,0000,0000,,Just like this, it seems I must break
Dialogue: 0,0:00:34.46,0:00:41.37,SR OP,,0000,0000,0000,,There are too many of these indescribable feelings
Dialogue: 0,0:00:41.37,0:00:48.21,SR OP,,0000,0000,0000,,I cannot deliver them to you, though you are near, the distance is great
Dialogue: 0,0:00:50.02,0:00:57.03,SR OP,,0000,0000,0000,,Forever only looking up at the blue sky is no good
Dialogue: 0,0:00:57.03,0:01:04.26,SR OP,,0000,0000,0000,,Spinning around (spinning around)…
Dialogue: 0,0:01:04.26,0:01:11.67,SR OP,,0000,0000,0000,,Unsteadily mustering strength, I want to try diving into your heart
Dialogue: 0,0:01:11.67,0:01:18.84,SR OP,,0000,0000,0000,,Spinning around (spinning around)…
Dialogue: 0,0:01:19.20,0:01:28.29,SR OP,,0000,0000,0000,,Lightly floating, again today I am alone above the clouds
Dialogue: 0,0:01:38.91,0:01:42.90,title-tl,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(320,170)\c&H306EE1&}Please, God!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:38.90,0:01:42.90,title-tl,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(320,290)\c&H306EE1&}Please, Real Animal Divination!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:38.90,0:01:42.91,title-tl,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(320,415)\c&H306EE1&}Please, Tenma!
