Dialogue: 0,0:01:59.26,0:02:01.75,SR main,,0000,0000,0000,,What’s the matter, Suou,\Nare you sleepy?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:01.75,0:02:04.53,SR main,,0000,0000,0000,,It looks like you’re cramming\Nand studying hard.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:04.53,0:02:05.62,SR main,,0000,0000,0000,,Shut up!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:11.04,0:02:13.74,SR main,,0000,0000,0000,,See? I told you so.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:16.34,0:02:17.61,SR main,,0000,0000,0000,,It’s because your heart’s not in it.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:18.57,0:02:22.61,SR main,,0000,0000,0000,,In the first place, why am I\Nthe partner in your practice?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:24.50,0:02:26.88,SR main,,0000,0000,0000,,I’ll be fine. This is nothing!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:26.88,0:02:28.29,SR main,,0000,0000,0000,,It seems that way…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.90,0:02:38.57,SR main,,0000,0000,0000,,It’s probably true that\Nmy heart wasn’t in it.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.57,0:02:41.05,SR main,,0000,0000,0000,,Who would have thought\Nthis pain would get worse…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.58,0:02:54.25,SR main,,0000,0000,0000,,It’s getting worse and worse.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.25,0:02:56.94,SR main,,0000,0000,0000,,What if I can’t hold a pencil?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.36,0:03:08.58,SR main,,0000,0000,0000,,It’s not like me to ask\Nthe gods for help, but…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.58,0:03:09.58,SR main,,0000,0000,0000,,Please!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.20,0:03:16.07,SR main,,0000,0000,0000,,I… I want to go to\Nthe same university as him!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.97,0:03:20.07,SR main,,0000,0000,0000,,I’m not that smart, though…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.07,0:03:23.51,SR main,,0000,0000,0000,,So, I can’t fail the test tomorrow!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.28,0:03:26.22,SR main,,0000,0000,0000,,I’m not asking for a good score!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.59,0:03:30.48,SR main,,0000,0000,0000,,At least let me hold a pencil\Nuntil the end of the test…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.23,0:03:39.89,SR main,,0000,0000,0000,,I can’t believe I’m doing this!\NSo unlike me!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.89,0:03:43.63,SR main,,0000,0000,0000,,Doing something like this…\NIt can’t possibly go the way I hope.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.23,0:03:51.00,SR main,,0000,0000,0000,,Is somebody here?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.91,0:03:58.05,SR main,,0000,0000,0000,,It can’t be…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.49,0:04:01.77,SR main,,0000,0000,0000,,Child, hold out thy hand and thy pencil.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.28,0:04:15.94,SR main,,0000,0000,0000,,How about that? You can\Nwrite with that, can’t you?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.43,0:04:19.40,SR main,,0000,0000,0000,,Set your mind at ease and go forth to thy school.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.87,0:04:21.59,SR main,,0000,0000,0000,,Th-Thank you…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.31,0:04:23.20,SR main,,0000,0000,0000,,Rather,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.64,0:04:25.54,SR main,,0000,0000,0000,,what are you doing, Harima?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.54,0:04:30.04,SR main,,0000,0000,0000,,What are you saying? I am\Nthe god living in this area.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.04,0:04:33.04,SR main,,0000,0000,0000,,Your sincere plea touched me, so I especially—
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.04,0:04:34.29,SR main,,0000,0000,0000,,No, you’re Harima!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.71,0:04:43.09,SR main,,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you, God!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.39,0:04:46.59,SR main,,0000,0000,0000,,And come to school already!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.06,0:04:50.53,SR main,,0000,0000,0000,,School…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.01,0:05:07.07,SR main,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, did you hear about\Nthe popular fortune-teller?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.50,0:05:08.62,SR main,,0000,0000,0000,,Fortune?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.35,0:05:11.85,SR main,,0000,0000,0000,,Ah, you mean the guy\Nwith the black sunglasses?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.85,0:05:13.72,SR main,,0000,0000,0000,,The one who has a place\Nin front of the station?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.72,0:05:16.12,SR main,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, yeah. Have you ever seen him?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.12,0:05:20.03,SR main,,0000,0000,0000,,No, but… the rumor\Nis that he never misses.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.03,0:05:23.70,SR main,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, I’d like to give a try, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.70,0:05:26.52,SR main,,0000,0000,0000,,I love fortune telling, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.52,0:05:29.54,SR main,,0000,0000,0000,,But when I’m told something bad, it bothers me.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.54,0:05:32.07,SR main,,0000,0000,0000,,You can just listen to the good things.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.07,0:05:33.68,SR main,,0000,0000,0000,,That’s the inviolable\Nrule of fortune telling.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.68,0:05:35.52,SR main,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh… Is that so…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.52,0:05:37.98,SR main,,0000,0000,0000,,What about you, Takano?\NAren’t you interested?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.36,0:05:40.21,SR main,,0000,0000,0000,,No, not that much.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.21,0:05:43.38,SR main,,0000,0000,0000,,By the way, don’t you have\Nto hurry? It’s lunchtime.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.86,0:05:49.66,SR main,,0000,0000,0000,,Wait, Karasuma-kun!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.90,0:05:56.62,SR main,,0000,0000,0000,,Rice balls again?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.92,0:05:59.40,SR main,,0000,0000,0000,,They’re rice balls…\NShe is making no progress.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.40,0:06:02.34,SR main,,0000,0000,0000,,But she messed up the curry.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.62,0:06:05.51,SR main,,0000,0000,0000,,When things go this bad, it’s time\Nfor the rest of us to make it happen.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.51,0:06:06.84,SR main,,0000,0000,0000,,Make what happen?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.50,0:06:10.05,SR main,,0000,0000,0000,,You’re going to help out,\Naren’t you, Fuyuki-kun?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.04,0:06:12.05,SR main,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.85,0:06:21.02,SR main,,0000,0000,0000,,This is some coincidence! We were just\Ntalking about going to a curry restaurant.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.02,0:06:24.69,SR main,,0000,0000,0000,,when Karasuma-kun and Fuyuki were \nalready on their way to the restaurant.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.69,0:06:26.53,SR main,,0000,0000,0000,,It really is a coincidence.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.53,0:06:29.79,SR main,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah! It feels like fate!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.22,0:06:37.21,SR main,,0000,0000,0000,,What’s the matter, Fuyuki-kun?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.21,0:06:40.88,SR main,,0000,0000,0000,,My stomach is a little…\NI’m going to pass today.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.88,0:06:44.31,SR main,,0000,0000,0000,,Ah, I had to go someplace\Non the way home.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.31,0:06:46.71,SR main,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, yeah, I was on a diet.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.71,0:06:48.88,SR main,,0000,0000,0000,,Come to think of it, it was\Nmy great grandmother’s last request
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.88,0:06:51.14,SR main,,0000,0000,0000,,that we not eat curry\Non her memorial day…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.72,0:06:56.12,SR main,,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry, Tsukamoto. See you later!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.42,0:07:02.38,SR main,,0000,0000,0000,,U-Umm, Karasuma-kun…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.38,0:07:03.31,SR main,,0000,0000,0000,,Let’s go.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.77,0:07:14.31,SR main,,0000,0000,0000,,Looks like it went well.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.31,0:07:15.51,SR main,,0000,0000,0000,,We did it!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.51,0:07:18.47,SR main,,0000,0000,0000,,Geez, what a troublesome couple.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.64,0:07:22.52,SR main,,0000,0000,0000,,Say, since we’re together,\Nwhy don’t we go for coffee?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.52,0:07:24.42,SR main,,0000,0000,0000,,If you’re treating.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.42,0:07:25.17,SR main,,0000,0000,0000,,Yikes.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.17,0:07:26.35,SR main,,0000,0000,0000,,Okay!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.37,0:07:31.05,SR main,,0000,0000,0000,,I really do have someplace\Nto go. Sorry, next time.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.00,0:07:37.35,SR main,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, shall the rest of us go?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.37,0:07:42.19,SR main,,0000,0000,0000,,What’s that? A fortune-teller?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.45,0:07:43.80,SR main,,0000,0000,0000,,It looks like it…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.23,0:07:48.19,Signs,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fsp1\fs10\c&H272C25&\bord0\b1\pos(324,396)\fnPeople Are People\clip(m 324 379 l 326 403 268 407 271 381)}real animal divination
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.74,0:07:46.29,SR main,,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you very much.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.29,0:07:48.15,SR main,,0000,0000,0000,,Now my company will recover.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.19,0:07:48.73,Signs,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fsp1\fs50\bord0\fnPeople Are People\c&H202622&\move(325,402,325,520)}real animal divination
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.69,0:07:53.41,SR main,,0000,0000,0000,,No, I just relay what these animals tell me.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.71,0:07:54.95,SR main,,0000,0000,0000,,Right, guys?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.39,0:08:00.02,SR main,,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you very much.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.99,0:08:07.13,SR main,,0000,0000,0000,,Excuse me, I’d like you\Nto tell me my fortune.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.66,0:08:11.10,SR main,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh? Have we met somewhere?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.10,0:08:15.34,SR main,,0000,0000,0000,,I don’t think so. I have a common face,\Nso it’s probably coincidental.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.34,0:08:19.64,SR main,,0000,0000,0000,,Probably. I don’t have anyone\Nso strange in my circle of friends.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.01,0:08:24.40,SR main,,0000,0000,0000,,N-Never mind that, what did\Nyou want me to forecast?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.73,0:08:30.18,SR main,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, I guess family fortune would cover it.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.18,0:08:31.69,SR main,,0000,0000,0000,,Can you forecast something like that?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.06,0:08:36.69,SR main,,0000,0000,0000,,There is nothing I don’t know.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.69,0:08:40.82,SR main,,0000,0000,0000,,I overcame great sorrow\Nand gained enlightenment.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.30,0:08:43.62,SR main,,0000,0000,0000,,Everything they say is the truth.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.20,0:08:46.13,SR main,,0000,0000,0000,,The animals do not betray.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.55,0:08:48.67,SR main,,0000,0000,0000,,Now, ask me anything!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.13,0:08:53.59,SR main,,0000,0000,0000,,O-Okay, then…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.04,0:08:56.94,SR main,,0000,0000,0000,,What is my father’s favorite food?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.59,0:08:57.80,Signs,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(0,600)\bord0\fs100\t(\fs40)\c&H202622&\fnVAGRundschriftD\move(103,172,482,51)}Ribbit
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.76,0:08:58.80,SR main,,0000,0000,0000,,It’s curry.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.80,0:09:00.98,SR main,,0000,0000,0000,,Do a serious reading!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.98,0:09:05.18,SR main,,0000,0000,0000,,B-But Alexander the frog is a very good.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.21,0:09:08.28,SR main,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, whatever. Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.98,0:09:16.35,SR main,,0000,0000,0000,,And you, rather than fooling around here, come to school, okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.63,0:09:23.98,SR main,,0000,0000,0000,,School? It all seems like so long ago.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.51,0:09:28.21,SR main,,0000,0000,0000,,I feel like I’ve washed away\Nthe filth from this world.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.82,0:09:31.11,SR main,,0000,0000,0000,,Now, I have these animals.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.11,0:09:35.22,SR main,,0000,0000,0000,,If I saw Tenma-chan now,\NI probably wouldn’t be impressed.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.68,0:09:38.18,SR main,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes… I’ve been reborn!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.57,0:09:41.93,SR main,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, look, look, Karasuma-kun!\NA fortune-teller!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.14,0:09:48.98,SR main,,0000,0000,0000,,Calm down! Calm down, you guys!
