Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.15,0:09:58.11,SR main,,0000,0000,0000,,This must be the one that Eri-chan and the others\Nmentioned whose predictions come true.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.60,0:10:01.37,SR main,,0000,0000,0000,,Please read my fortune.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.64,0:10:06.12,SR main,,0000,0000,0000,,Your fortune in l-love?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.31,0:10:09.05,SR main,,0000,0000,0000,,N-No!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.05,0:10:13.38,SR main,,0000,0000,0000,,We’re not seeing each other or anything.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.72,0:10:17.59,SR main,,0000,0000,0000,,I-I see, they’re not dating yet.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.89,0:10:22.23,SR main,,0000,0000,0000,,No, but since you mentioned it, if you will?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.23,0:10:24.39,SR main,,0000,0000,0000,,Fortune in love.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.14,0:10:28.70,SR main,,0000,0000,0000,,Al… right. I’ll read your fortune.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.70,0:10:30.32,SR main,,0000,0000,0000,,Yay!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.32,0:10:31.73,SR main,,0000,0000,0000,,Please!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.91,0:10:34.68,SR main,,0000,0000,0000,,What shall I do…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.68,0:10:37.13,SR main,,0000,0000,0000,,Maybe I’ll tell her their\Ncompatibility is the worst.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.59,0:10:40.95,SR main,,0000,0000,0000,,N-No, I mustn’t! I’ve already given up this world.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.08,0:10:46.41,SR main,,0000,0000,0000,,I’ve decided not to let love bewilder me… But…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.08,0:10:43.65,SR second,,0000,0000,0000,,Let’s go for curry after this, okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.65,0:10:46.41,SR second,,0000,0000,0000,,After all, you love curry, don’t you?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.41,0:10:50.92,SR second,,0000,0000,0000,,I’m really looking forward to it.\NI want to hurry and have that curry!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.92,0:10:54.41,SR main,,0000,0000,0000,,Say, which do you like better,\Nbeef and potatoes, or curry?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.41,0:10:55.32,SR main,,0000,0000,0000,,Curry.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.93,0:11:05.37,SR main,,0000,0000,0000,,Ah… Umm… Then, which do you\Nlike better, m-m-me or curry?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.37,0:11:06.35,SR main,,0000,0000,0000,,Curry.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.58,0:11:14.25,SR main,,0000,0000,0000,,Ah… Umm… Maybe I asked it wrong.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.25,0:11:17.14,SR main,,0000,0000,0000,,Which do you like better,\Nprepackaged curry or me?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.86,0:11:27.96,SR main,,0000,0000,0000,,He hesitated!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.96,0:11:30.96,SR main,,0000,0000,0000,,Karasuma-kun hesitated choosing between\Nme and prepackaged curry!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.65,0:11:34.93,SR main,,0000,0000,0000,,Wait a minute, you!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.08,0:11:42.63,SR main,,0000,0000,0000,,I won’t forgive you, Nijou…\NI mean, Karasuma!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.41,0:11:46.39,SR main,,0000,0000,0000,,Maybe it’s none of my business, but…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.95,0:11:51.06,SR main,,0000,0000,0000,,When a woman cries right\Nin front of me, I can’t let it go!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.42,0:11:54.52,SR main,,0000,0000,0000,,The Angry Fist! I mean, Kick!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.56,0:12:03.66,SR main,,0000,0000,0000,,Go after her.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.03,0:12:07.37,SR main,,0000,0000,0000,,You’re telling me to go after her?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.70,0:12:10.53,SR main,,0000,0000,0000,,What… What in the world\Nare you thinking, Karasuma?!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.06,0:12:16.46,SR main,,0000,0000,0000,,I… can’t go after her.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.46,0:12:18.92,note,,0000,0000,0000,,Curry Shop
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.92,0:12:20.42,note,,0000,0000,0000,,Everything Half Price
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.48,0:12:23.68,SR main,,0000,0000,0000,,I understand!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.11,0:12:52.20,SR main,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, he fell all the way down!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.85,0:12:54.36,SR main,,0000,0000,0000,,I wonder if he’s okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.85,0:12:59.72,SR main,,0000,0000,0000,,Wow, he left just like that.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.71,0:13:08.01,SR main,,0000,0000,0000,,All this time…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.47,0:13:12.83,SR main,,0000,0000,0000,,All this time…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.53,0:13:19.82,SR main,,0000,0000,0000,,All this time… I’ve…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.81,0:13:23.37,SR main,,0000,0000,0000,,watched you.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.58,0:13:27.48,SR main,,0000,0000,0000,,Harima-kun.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.33,0:13:43.69,SR main,,0000,0000,0000,,No good… I… can’t run any further…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.33,0:13:46.84,SR main,,0000,0000,0000,,Is it all going to end here?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.72,0:13:53.27,SR main,,0000,0000,0000,,T-Tenma-chan?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.51,0:13:56.48,SR main,,0000,0000,0000,,C-Could… such a thing happen?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.51,0:13:59.72,SR main,,0000,0000,0000,,Hear me out!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.72,0:14:03.02,SR main,,0000,0000,0000,,I’ve… loved you since we first me!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.78,0:14:07.03,SR main,,0000,0000,0000,,I finally… finally said it!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.30,0:14:22.42,SR main,,0000,0000,0000,,I wonder if Tsukamoto was\Nable to be alone with him.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.97,0:14:25.97,SR main,,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry for all the trouble,\Nmaking you help us and all.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.97,0:14:27.54,SR main,,0000,0000,0000,,It’s okay, it’s okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.54,0:14:30.48,SR main,,0000,0000,0000,,Your set up was magnificent, Takano.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.48,0:14:33.81,SR main,,0000,0000,0000,,Just let me know and\NI’ll help you out, too, Mikoto-san.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.32,0:14:35.89,SR main,,0000,0000,0000,,I don’t need it!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.19,0:14:40.32,SR main,,0000,0000,0000,,Who is it that you like, Suou-san?!\NDo you know, Takano-san?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.74,0:14:41.82,SR main,,0000,0000,0000,,Of course!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.82,0:14:45.36,SR main,,0000,0000,0000,,What?! What are you\Ntalking about, Takano?!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.42,0:14:49.50,SR main,,0000,0000,0000,,D-Do-Don’t you say anything! Geez!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.50,0:14:51.00,SR main,,0000,0000,0000,,I’m just joking.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.00,0:14:53.37,SR main,,0000,0000,0000,,I’m afraid you just might do it!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.67,0:14:57.06,SR main,,0000,0000,0000,,But you should do whatever you can.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.06,0:15:00.79,SR main,,0000,0000,0000,,Cowardly love will only mean regrets.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.11,0:15:04.44,SR main,,0000,0000,0000,,Come to think of it, I’ve never heard\Nthat sort of story about Sawachika-san.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.44,0:15:05.55,SR main,,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.11,0:15:08.45,SR main,,0000,0000,0000,,She’s always with some guy or other.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.45,0:15:11.79,SR main,,0000,0000,0000,,Those are all the guys\Nwho are after her, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.79,0:15:14.45,SR main,,0000,0000,0000,,I’ve never heard of her formally\Nseeing anyone in particular.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.45,0:15:16.52,SR main,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, I guess that’s true.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.93,0:15:21.02,SR main,,0000,0000,0000,,I was just wondering if she’s\Never fallen for a guy herself.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.63,0:15:25.15,SR main,,0000,0000,0000,,I love you.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.30,0:15:30.47,SR main,,0000,0000,0000,,Why do you laugh?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.47,0:15:32.61,SR main,,0000,0000,0000,,That image just seems way off the mark.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.11,0:15:35.73,SR main,,0000,0000,0000,,I mean, seriously!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.81,0:15:43.41,SR main,,0000,0000,0000,,In the first place, I can’t imagine\Nat all, what kind of guy it would be.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.82,0:15:48.99,SR main,,0000,0000,0000,,Shall we take another way home?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.99,0:15:50.58,SR main,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, good idea.
