Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.23,0:16:06.66,SR main,,0000,0000,0000,,Um… I… don’t know what to say…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.66,0:16:08.91,SR main,,0000,0000,0000,,Hario!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.30,0:16:12.29,SR main,,0000,0000,0000,,I looked all over for you.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.83,0:16:16.21,SR main,,0000,0000,0000,,Tonight’s dinner is my special\Nhome-made beef and potatoes.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.49,0:16:17.71,SR main,,0000,0000,0000,,It’s really good.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.99,0:16:19.95,SR main,,0000,0000,0000,,Come on, let’s go home.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.66,0:16:24.32,SR main,,0000,0000,0000,,Wait, Harima-kun.
