Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.93,0:16:44.89,SR main,,0000,0000,0000,,What was that girl so mad about?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.35,0:16:47.22,SR main,,0000,0000,0000,,I don’t know for sure,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.22,0:16:51.36,SR main,,0000,0000,0000,,but she’s from a very rich family,\Nso she doesn’t like people like me!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.86,0:16:54.36,SR main,,0000,0000,0000,,But, thanks to her,\NI’ve snapped out of it.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.70,0:17:00.08,SR main,,0000,0000,0000,,Tomorrow… I’ll confess\Nmy feelings to the one I love.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.47,0:17:04.20,SR main,,0000,0000,0000,,Then if she turns me down, I’ll quit school.
