Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.78,0:17:24.07,SR main,,0000,0000,0000,,It’s alright. I entered the\Nschool to be with her.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.07,0:17:25.44,SR main,,0000,0000,0000,,At this point…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.62,0:17:31.46,SR main,,0000,0000,0000,,Is that so… Then,\Nyou’ll leave this place, too?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.46,0:17:34.44,SR main,,0000,0000,0000,,If you like, you can\Nstay a little longer.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.55,0:17:40.49,SR main,,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you for taking care\Nof me up until now.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.47,0:17:50.45,SR main,,0000,0000,0000,,It was nice having someone\Nhere when I came home.
