Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.97,0:19:57.30,Riding the wind,,0000,0000,0000,,The ﬁrst time I saw you,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.30,0:20:02.04,Riding the wind,,0000,0000,0000,,you stole my heart, didn’t you?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.14,0:20:08.48,Riding the wind,,0000,0000,0000,,I saw only you all this time.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.48,0:20:12.98,Riding the wind,,0000,0000,0000,,It is my ﬁrst confession of love.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.36,0:20:21.06,Riding the wind,,0000,0000,0000,,The other day, I made a slight mistake,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.06,0:20:24.33,Riding the wind,,0000,0000,0000,,but please don’t mind.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.33,0:20:27.77,Riding the wind,,0000,0000,0000,,This is the ﬁrst and last chance!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.77,0:20:33.71,Riding the wind,,0000,0000,0000,,For my love to ride the wind to you.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.71,0:20:39.68,Riding the wind,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(0,500)}I love you.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:41.52,0:20:45.61,SR main,,0000,0000,0000,,Knowing my true feelings,\Nhow will you react?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.19,0:20:51.49,SR main,,0000,0000,0000,,Ha-Harima-kun, umm… you know…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.98,0:20:54.89,SR main,,0000,0000,0000,,Here!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.89,0:20:58.15,SR main,,0000,0000,0000,,Your letter of resignation was for some reason in my shoebox.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:59.77,0:21:03.83,SR main,,0000,0000,0000,,I made a mistake!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:05.14,0:21:07.31,SR main,,0000,0000,0000,,I… I mixed up the contents!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:07.31,0:21:09.61,SR main,,0000,0000,0000,,Harima-kun, what’s the matter?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:10.48,0:21:13.07,SR main,,0000,0000,0000,,My love is over.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:14.53,0:21:18.32,SR main,,0000,0000,0000,,Say, Harima-kun, I don’t like it this way.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:20.26,0:21:22.89,SR main,,0000,0000,0000,,Come to school, Harima-kun.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:23.81,0:21:24.82,SR main,,0000,0000,0000,,Okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:25.16,0:21:25.99,SR main,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes.
