Dialogue: 0,0:21:27.27,0:21:28.39,SR main,,0000,0000,0000,,Tani-sensei
Dialogue: 0,0:21:29.46,0:21:31.00,SR main,,0000,0000,0000,,I found this outside.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:32.33,0:21:34.89,SR main,,0000,0000,0000,,From Harima? What could it be?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:37.94,0:21:41.24,SR main,,0000,0000,0000,,After all that’s happened,\NI’ve come back.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:42.86,0:21:44.86,SR main,,0000,0000,0000,,Who are you?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:48.32,0:21:54.41,SR ED,,0000,0000,0000,,Boys are always chasing after girls
Dialogue: 0,0:21:54.41,0:22:00.17,SR ED,,0000,0000,0000,,All day long they’re thinking of girls
Dialogue: 0,0:22:00.17,0:22:04.87,SR ED,,0000,0000,0000,,But those boys certainly are a little stupid,
Dialogue: 0,0:22:04.87,0:22:10.34,SR ED,,0000,0000,0000,,They never seem to understand girls’ feelings
Dialogue: 0,0:22:11.79,0:22:14.96,SR ED,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, you really really are a big dummy
Dialogue: 0,0:22:14.96,0:22:17.63,SR ED,,0000,0000,0000,,Shall I give you a lesson, Big Dummy?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:17.63,0:22:21.02,SR ED,,0000,0000,0000,,So, the most important thing in the world is…
Dialogue: 0,0:22:21.02,0:22:23.87,SR ED,,0000,0000,0000,,The thing that absolutely must be…
Dialogue: 0,0:22:23.87,0:22:28.31,SR ED,,0000,0000,0000,,It’s definitely “timing”, you see?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:29.48,0:22:31.45,SR ED,,0000,0000,0000,,So, if you wanna say “I love you”,
Dialogue: 0,0:22:31.45,0:22:34.64,SR ED,,0000,0000,0000,,Go on a date, or do something…
Dialogue: 0,0:22:35.32,0:22:40.65,SR ED,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, kiss, or say goodbye, at any time…
Dialogue: 0,0:22:41.32,0:22:44.66,SR ED,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, the most important thing in the world is
Dialogue: 0,0:22:44.66,0:22:49.57,SR ED,,0000,0000,0000,,definitely “timing”, I think, but…
Dialogue: 0,0:22:49.57,0:22:50.55,SR ED,,0000,0000,0000,,Or something
